NLWPork10.First Lines:
A hart harborowthA knyȝt herborovtheA Boke logytheA
                    squyer logythe…
NLWPork10.Last Lines:
…A Cheynen fynnydeA Perche and a roche I schallydA Tenche
                    in lollyA Plays I savssyd

YaleBei365.Note:
Partly in code of vowels represented by the letter in alphabet that
                    follows them (‘f’ for ‘e’, ‘p’ for
                    ‘o’, etc.).
